--- MYSQLTR ---

HOWTO:

Read the wiki page for more detailed instructions: https://sourceforge.net/p/mysqltr/wiki/Home/

Unpack the project:
$ tar -xvzf mysqltr-0.1.zip

Change the directory:
$ cd ./mysqltr-0.1/

Edit/add regular expressions for custom filters
$ vim ./filters/filter.sed

Convert your database:
$ ./mysqltr --from=user@127.0.0.1:3306/database1 --to=user@127.0.0.1:3306/database2

